com.company.model.entity

Class MealToDisplay

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.company.model.entity.MealToDisplay
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class MealToDisplay
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class is used to show meal entries and meal TOTAL values to user. It contains: mealType name and product name instead of their id; calories, protein, fat and carbs of the product according to its weight (not for 100 grams)
